Pitfalls

Added 'pitfalls' to the Windows SDK section. I read this page, attempted to compile for Android, and then discovered these issues the hard way. Spaces in pathnames are bad news with cygwin; first I had the android-ndk in a location with spaces, and then the project source itself. When configuring the Android SDK, version 1.6 must be added; my build for 2.0.1 failed to complete (at 'ant install') until I realized this. Ftg2 05:24, 10 June 2010 (UTC)
